{"tid":911781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"城大又有人嘈","createTime":"2018-11-22T07:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T07:34:10.000Z","uid":160342,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4886a9647e5db85481844dbf77eca26331705f2","tid":911781,"uid":160342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"今日經過ac 1，有條友好大聲屌柒某個斯斯文文嘅男仔 <br />\n又督晒枱又講晒粗口，睇個勢差少少又反枱 <br />\n之後佢比個啊伯屌反轉頭 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伯 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌人果個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望咩柒啊 鬧緊人啊 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細聲啲啊 你騷擾緊人  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關唔關你事啊 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你騷擾我啊 唔關我事 咁大聲鬧人做咩啊 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢唔知醜嘛 我教緊佢啊 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你知唔知啊 你教人還教人 唔好騷擾人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後個學生收左皮<br />\n認真啊伯一隻粗口都無講已經震撼左全場人 <br />\n勁<br />\n<br />\n唔知咩事，但公眾地方大大聲講粗口屌柒人真心柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4f9996b115ae53fb166df1746af930063fdecd","tid":911781,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"讀屎片"},{"pid":"a51c773063f7834e15a2de08c2c779e33e88a716","tid":911781,"uid":161741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"有教養<br />\n冇教養"},{"pid":"42d9be3ebc49b88b455cf6857070c78bc79e57a3","tid":911781,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"說個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=